    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The suspension retains its original damping profile with zero bushing deflection, while the cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers provide fade-free deceleration. This is a true collector-grade specimen with a laser-straight chassis, untouched factory welds, and a pristine interior.",
