      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera in Arctic Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and the condition reflects a lifetime of obsessive care. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the supple black leather remains taut and smells factory-fresh, with no wear on the seat bolsters or thinning of the carpets. Mechanically, this 911 is peerless; the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced, and the car comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record since its original delivery. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions perfectly. From the pristine underside to the untouched tool kit in the trunk, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
